{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"fb563cffdb15e70e500879","title":"组一：仅打印开始 / 结束时间（上一版全局参数）","desc":"","updated":1780371367065,"created":1780371330029,"custom":{},"fname":"打印数据.01-上一版-仅开始结束时间","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"7f5ab15f6a70a3de0bf0eaf21fcba5fe","links":[{"from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":54,"column":3,"offset":1226},"end":{"line":54,"column":26,"offset":1249},"indent":[]},"value":"打印数据.01-上一版-仅开始结束时间"}],"anchors":{"组一仅打印开始--结束时间上一版全局参数":{"type":"header","text":"组一：仅打印开始 / 结束时间（上一版全局参数）","value":"组一仅打印开始--结束时间上一版全局参数","line":8,"column":0,"depth":1},"纸上应出现的内容":{"type":"header","text":"纸上应出现的内容","value":"纸上应出现的内容","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"用途":{"type":"header","text":"用途","value":"用途","line":22,"column":0,"depth":2},"上一版无-modes-页脚时speed5-全局参数纪要":{"type":"header","text":"上一版（无 Modes 页脚时）speed=5 全局参数纪要","value":"上一版无-modes-页脚时speed5-全局参数纪要","line":26,"column":0,"depth":2},"归档建议":{"type":"header","text":"归档建议","value":"归档建议","line":42,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"b214abeb9f8f17aa994522","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"组一仅打印开始--结束时间上一版全局参数\">组一：仅打印开始 / 结束时间（上一版全局参数）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#组一仅打印开始--结束时间上一版全局参数\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"组一仅打印开始--结束时间上一版全局参数-1\">组一：仅打印开始 / 结束时间（上一版全局参数）<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#组一仅打印开始--结束时间上一版全局参数-1\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"纸上应出现的内容\">纸上应出现的内容<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#纸上应出现的内容\"></a></h2>\n<p>仅三行测速信息，例如：</p>\n<pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">S:12345\nE:14123\nC:1778ms\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>不应出现</strong> <code>Modes:</code> 及六种模式名列表。</p>\n<h2 id=\"用途\">用途<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#用途\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>与「本版」样张对比时，可排除「模式列表占用少量走纸/文字时间」的差异，主要看<strong>同一套图像</strong>在旧全局参数下的 <code>C</code> 值。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"上一版无-modes-页脚时speed5-全局参数纪要\">上一版（无 Modes 页脚时）speed=5 全局参数纪要<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#上一版无-modes-页脚时speed5-全局参数纪要\"></a></h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>以下为与当前仓库对比的「上一版」快照，对应 <code>thermal_printer_print_bitmap</code> 内仍只有 <code>S/E/C</code> 三行、尚未调用 <code>lv_desktop_format_print_footer</code> 时的参数量级。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"table-responsive\">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<table><thead><tr><th>项</th><th>数值</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>inter_group_us</code></td><td>1</td></tr><tr><td><code>line_cooling_us</code></td><td>12</td></tr><tr><td><code>heat_us_at_5c / 25c / 40c</code></td><td>1120 / 980 / 860</td></tr><tr><td><code>motor_step_us</code></td><td>680</td></tr><tr><td><code>status_check_period_lines</code></td><td>80</td></tr><tr><td>连续白行批量上限</td><td>64</td></tr><tr><td>周期性 <code>rt_thread_mdelay(1)</code></td><td>约每 128 行</td></tr><tr><td>位图结束后 <code>thermal_printer_feed</code></td><td>2</td></tr><tr><td>高密度行额外加热（黑点档）</td><td>+170 / +115 / +70 / +38 / +14（分档）</td></tr></tbody></table></div>\n<h2 id=\"归档建议\">归档建议<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#归档建议\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>文件名建议：<code>YYYYMMDD_模式名_仅SEC_备注.jpg</code>（模式名仅作你当时 UI 记录，该版纸上不打印模式）。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/\">root</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"root","desc":"BK7252N AI 打印机固件文档库","updated":1780371367067,"created":1595961348801,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"notes","name":"Dendron"},"contentHash":"e5d7823b7368b844c5d7bde821080751","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"root","vaultName":"Dendron"},"value":"开发记录.项目开发记录总纲","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":83},"end":{"line":8,"column":20,"offset":100},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"开发记录.项目开发记录总纲"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"ro